    "name": "STRAFTAT",
    "steam_appid": 2386720,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386720/extras/547cf71da4474778fb1bf4d109e03496.poster.avif?t=1764157677\" width=614 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386720/extras/547cf71da4474778fb1bf4d109e03496.webm?t=1764157677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386720/extras/547cf71da4474778fb1bf4d109e03496.mp4?t=1764157677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Straftat》是一款免费游玩的在线第一人称射击游戏，支持临近语音聊天，可进行 1v1、2v2 或自由混战（FFA）模式。游戏拥有种类繁多的地图，以及丰富的火器、爆炸物和近战武器可供选择。  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一场比赛由多个回合组成。当场上只剩下一名幸存者时，该回合结束。</strong><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386720/extras/7b16f3a5d569384f1413ea9e20273441.poster.avif?t=1764157677\" width=614 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386720/extras/7b16f3a5d569384f1413ea9e20273441.webm?t=1764157677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386720/extras/7b16f3a5d569384f1413ea9e20273441.mp4?t=1764157677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每个回合都会在不同的环境中进行。</strong><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Straftat》拥有超过 350 个可供游玩的竞技场。</strong>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386720/extras/17cca522b2e3af455ed01bdda3e5095e.poster.avif?t=1764157677\" width=614 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386720/extras/17cca522b2e3af455ed01bdda3e5095e.webm?t=1764157677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386720/extras/17cca522b2e3af455ed01bdda3e5095e.mp4?t=1764157677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每张地图都有自己独特的武器配置。</strong><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拾取武器，狩猎你的对手。</strong><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386720/extras/2520a26d4fa8ae96e943aab1b5f1018f.poster.avif?t=1764157677\" width=614 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386720/extras/2520a26d4fa8ae96e943aab1b5f1018f.webm?t=1764157677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386720/extras/2520a26d4fa8ae96e943aab1b5f1018f.mp4?t=1764157677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>通过完成独特挑战解锁帽子与时尚装饰品。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>支持键盘与手柄操作。</strong></i></u></h2>",
